  "bodyText": "Skip to main content\nGizmoo AI\nFeatures\nDemo\nUse Cases\nPricing\nFAQ\nSign In\nGet Started\nNevermissanothercall.\n\nThe AI voice receptionist that answers every call, books every appointment, 24/7.\n\nStart Free Trial\nWatch Demo\n50,000+ calls\n99.7% satisfaction\n24/7\nSCROLL TO DISCOVER\n00 — ABOUT\nWhat is\nGizmoo AI?\n\nGizmoo AI is an Australian AI voice receptionist that answers business phone calls 24/7. It picks up every inbound call within seconds, qualifies the caller, books appointments directly into your calendar, and sends SMS confirmations — all without human intervention.\n\nUnlike traditional answering services, Gizmoo uses advanced conversational AI with natural-sounding speech and emotional intelligence. Most callers don't realize they're speaking with AI. When Gizmoo encounters something it can't handle, it seamlessly transfers with full context.\n\n50,000+\nCALLS ANSWERED\n99.7%\nSATISFACTION\n24/7/365\nAVAILABILITY\n30s\nAVG RESPONSE\n500+\nBUSINESSES\n15 min\nSETUP TIME\nHealthcare\nLegal\nReal Estate\nSalons & Spas\nHome Services\nHVAC\nPlumbing\nElectrical\nDental\nRestaurants\nAuto Repair\nInsurance\nProperty Management\nVeterinary\nHealthcare\nLegal\nReal Estate\nSalons & Spas\nHome Services\nHVAC\nPlumbing\nElectrical\nDental\nRestaurants\nAuto Repair\nInsurance\nProperty Management\nVeterinary\n01 — FEATURES\nSix things your new receptionist never sleeps on.\nAnswers Every Call\n\n24/7 instant pickup. Zero voicemail. Every call is answered within seconds, day or night, weekday or holiday. Your callers never hear a busy tone again.\n\n99.7%\nPICKUP RATE\nBooks Appointments\n\nReal-time scheduling with instant confirmations. Gizmoo checks availability, books the slot, sends SMS confirmations, and adds it to your calendar — all in one call.\n\n40%\nMORE BOOKINGS\nSyncs Your Calendar\n\nGoogle Calendar, Outlook, Calendly, Acuity, Cal.com, and 100+ more. Always synced, time-zone aware, never double-booked. Your schedule stays pristine.\n\n100+\nINTEGRATIONS\nMakes Outbound Calls\n\nAppointment reminders, follow-ups, and conf",
